# All automation in this directory is POSIX shell. Force LF line endings so the
# scripts run under Git Bash on Windows (a CRLF in the shebang breaks /usr/bin/env).
# The repo root uses `* text=auto`, which would otherwise apply CRLF on Windows checkout.
*.sh        text eol=lf
run_gates   text eol=lf
pre-commit  text eol=lf